name: MultiFi
description: The first multi-target dataset for DFL and HAR. It has 710 available positions for DFL and 22 daily actions for HAR. MultiFi also provides data collected from different environments. We believe our MultiFi will significantly contribute to device-free localization, human action recognition, human-computer interaction, and smart building research.
keywords: Wireless Sensing, Intelligent WiFi Sensing,Device-free localization, Human Action Recognition
